         <abstract id="aspace_b2074cfc9e65236312ce3fb9ed80c3e5">Lucia Pickering Wheatland married John Fulton, who was in Oxford on a Rhodes fellowship, in 1923. The collection contains correspondence from Lucia and John Fulton in Oxford to Lucia's parents, Richard and Mary Wheatland, in Massachusetts. John Fulton was named professor of physiology at Yale in 1929.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="ingest">
               <part>Fulton, Lucia Pickering</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
